If this is your first installation of Karybu, before we get started, you should know that we will need some information from you regarding your database setup.

These items should have been provided to you by your web service provider or your web admin, if not you can always ask for them and resume this installation later on.

A widget is a small free-standing application used in a layout or page module.
 It can be linked with internal module or external Open API. Through its configuration setting, wide application is possible. 
 You can directly add a widget by using the [Generate Code] function without using the Karybu page module or layout module.
